| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3049 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4054e8e0-21b8-5e94-8cb5-7cad4c392d0c"
